quran[8{c,v,t}:
10,71,"inn ko Nooh ka qissa sunaaoo, uss waqt ka qissa jab uss ne apni qoum se kaha tha ke “اے baradran qoum, agar mera tumahray darmain rehna aur Allah ki ayaat suna suna kar tumhe ghaflat se beedar karna tumahray liye na qabil bardasht ho gaya hai to mera bharosa Allah par hai, tum apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko sath le kar aik mutafiqa faisla kar lau aur jo mansoobah tumahray paish e nazar ho is ko khoob soch samajh lau taakay is ka ko yi pehlu tumhari nigah se posheeda nah rahay, phir mere khilaaf is ko amal mein le aao aur mujhe hargiz mohlat nah do"
10,72,"tum ne meri nasiyaat se mun morra ( to mera kya nuqsaan kya ) mein tum se kisi ajar ka talab gaar nah tha, mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke ( khuwa koi manay ya nah manay ) mein khud muslim ban kar rahon """
10,73,"unhon ne usay jhtlaya aur nateeja yeh howa ke hum ne usay aur unn logon ko jo is ke sath kashti mein thay, bacha liya aur unhi ko zameen mein janasheen banaya aur un sab logon ko ghark kar diya jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya tha pas dekh lau ke jinhein mutnabba kya gaya tha ( aur phir bhi unhon ne maan kar nah diya ) unn ka kya injaam howa"
10,74,"phir Nooh ke baad hum ne mukhtalif payghambaroon ko unn ki qomon ki taraf bheja aur woh unn ke paas khuli khuli nishanain le kar aeye, magar jis cheez ko unhon ne pehlay jhutla diya tha usay phir maan kar nah diya is terhan hum hadd se guzar jaane walon ke dilon par thp_h laga dete hain"
10,75,"phir un ke baad hum ne moose aur haroon ko apni nshanyon ke sath firaon aur is ke sardaro ki taraf bheja, magar unhon ne apni barayi ka ghamand kya aur woh mujrim log thay"
10,76,pas jab hamaray paas se haq un ke samnay aaya to unhon ne keh diya ke yeh to khula jaadoo hai
10,77,"moose ne kaha : “تم haq ko yeh kehte ho jabkay woh tumahray samnay agaya? kya yeh jaadoo hai? halaank jaadoo gir Falah nahi paaya karte """
10,78,"onhon ne jawab mein kaha “کیا twas liye aaya hai ke hamein aُ seen tareeqay se phair day jis par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai aur zameen mein barayi tum dono ki qaim ho jaye? tumahray baat to hum maan-ne walay nahi hain """
